Why this version is useful
A language-learning version helps you:
•	teach pronunciation in a repeatable way,
•	switch voices for different lesson styles,
•	use Firebase claims for sensitive or community-owned content,
•	keep the same codebase pattern across future apps.[google +1]
Important boundary
If you include Indigenous language content, keep it permission-based and culturally approved; the app should not infer, synthesize, or impersonate Indigenous voices without rights-holder and community approval
